OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1774271469
OL,3,CHorse sculptures installed on new
OL,4,Croundabout to celebrate equestrian
OL,5,Chistory
OL,7,FTwo steel sculptures of horses have
OL,8,Fbeen installed at a roundabout on the
OL,9,Fnew Carlisle Southern Link Road.
OL,11,FLocal artist Ellie Barden created the
OL,12,Fstatues out of weathered steel, which
OL,13,FCumberland Council claims will be
OL,14,F"durable and low maintenance".
OL,16,FThe artwork, entitled "The Mare and
OL,17,FFoal", is situated at the newly-
OL,18,Fconstructed Durdar roundabout, next to
OL,19,FCarlisle Racecourse.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
