PN,35702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1774271469
OL,3,CHorse sculptures installed on new
OL,4,Croundabout to celebrate equestrian
OL,5,Chistory
OL,7,FWeighing in at around four tonnes
OL,8,Feach, they were lowered into position
OL,9,Fby cranes.
OL,11,FAt another new roundabout on the Link
OL,12,FRoad, where the Cumberland Show was
OL,13,Fformerly held, a further steel statue
OL,14,Fhas been unveiled - the "Limousin
OL,15,FBull", inspired by a real bull which
OL,16,Fsold for a record 180,000 guineas in
OL,17,FMay 2022 at the Carlisle auction mart.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
