FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1774271469
OL,3,CHorse sculptures installed on new
OL,4,Croundabout to celebrate equestrian
OL,5,Chistory
OL,7,FCllr Denise Rollo, Cumberland
OL,8,FCouncil's Executive Member for
OL,9,FSustainable, Resilient and Connected
OL,10,FPlaces, said: "These sculptures are a
OL,11,Fcelebration of our local heritage and
OL,12,Fthe strong rural identity that
OL,13,Funderpins communities across
OL,14,FCumberland.
OL,16,F"They showcase the talent of a local
OL,17,Fartist, create distinct landmarks for
OL,18,Fthe new route, and reflect the pride
OL,19,Fwe have in our past and our ambitions
OL,20,Ffor the future.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
