PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1774271469
OL,3,CHorse sculptures installed on new
OL,4,Croundabout to celebrate equestrian
OL,5,Chistory
OL,7,F"The Carlisle Southern Link Road is
OL,8,Fmoving closer to completion, and these
OL,9,Finstallations mark a really exciting
OL,10,Fmoment in the project."
OL,12,FThe remaining sections of the link
OL,13,Froad are due to open after a road
OL,14,Fsafety review which is scheduled for
OL,15,FApril.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
